Ilul deg walef uttseε meyya usetta urebεin, di Agadu, deg yirebbi n yidurar n Neffusa, anẓul-amalu n tmurt n Libya n wass-a.
D ayen i t-iḥettmen ad yuɣal ɣer Trablus deg walef uttseε meyya usebεa usettin, ad iɣer azref, anda i d-iḥella agerdas n ubugaṭu.
Seg umezruy, ass n xemseṭṭac yunyu zuǧ alaf uttesεa, ugin yimḍebbren n tmurt n Merruk ad d-yettwasken i tɣamsa Udlis aberkan n Saɛid Sifaw deg Uqusis n Tɣamsa n Rribaṭ.
Yella ussan-a iɛeddan di Bgayet unemhal amatu n Uxxam aɣelnaw n yizerfan n umeskar d yizerfan inaragen Mass Sami Bencix, i lmend n usarag i d-iga deg usensu Crystal.
Mi d-yesmekta inaẓuren ɣef wazal n uḥuddu n yisnulfuyen-nsen sɣur Uxxam aɣelnaw n yizerfan n umeskar d yizerfan inaragen, yenna-d unemhal-is belli ihegga ad yesbedd di Bgayet aɣerbaz n tẓuriwin ɣer sdat, abeɛda ma ur d-mlalen ugur deg tifin n unnar anda ara yettwabnu.
Ad d-nesmekti d akken aṭas n tlufa iɣef i d-yemmeslay iseggasen-a ineggura unemhal ɣef wayen yerzan aqader n yizerfan n umeskar.
Ama d aẓawan neɣ d tugna, yenna-d Mass Bencix ilaq fell-asent ad ttxellisent izerfan n umeskar, akken ur yettili ccɣel d tukerḍa n uzref n unaẓur.
Dima deg ubrid n uḥuddu ɣef unaẓur d usnulfu n wallaɣ, isuter unemhal amatu n yizerfan n umeskar ula d takebbanit tameqqrant Google akken ad d-tettak izerfan i yinaẓuren i yesrusuyen di Youtube iqeddicen-nsen n tẓuri.
Xas ulamma tenna-d tneɣlaft n tjara d akken ssumat n lxuḍra, lfakya akked uksum ad subbent, maca deg unnar, nettwali d ayen-nniḍen i iḍerrun.
Ma yella wid teɛna temsalt di lwilaya, ilaq fell-asen ad d-ffɣen akken ad ɛassen wigi ixeddmen leswami akken i d asen-yehwa acku di yal tamnadt amek ara tent-tafeḍ, ur ɛdilent ara”.
Ma d aseqqamu-agi i bɣan ad sbedden d aleqqem d usejhed n yimenzayen n tɣamsa i d-yebder usaḍuf agmanan n uselɣu, i d-yeffɣen deg useggas n zuǧ alaf utnac.
Asuddis addalan n xemsin alef n yimukan n Tizi Uzzu, i d-tesfaydi terbaɛt n yilmeẓyen n Leqbayel, ad d-yewjed deg wakud i as-d-yettuɛeggnen,di taggara n waggur n ɣuct i d-iteddun.
Iberreḥ s waya, lwali n Tizi Uzzu Meḥmud Ǧemεa, i yerzan ɣur-s taggara n ddurt iɛeddan, anida i yessefqed aswir uɣur wwḍen lecɣal n usenfar-agi.
Ad d-nesmekti kan belli, deg waggur n meɣres iɛeddan i srekben yakan xemsin alef n yikersiwen n yimferǧen n unnar-agi meqqren, i d-igren s annar taluft n yisem-is.
Ma d aselway n terbaɛt n yelmezyen n Leqbayel, Crif Mellal, yemtawa d umsulɣu Guillaume Mulak iwakken ad yili d anemhal n usileɣ deg wammas n usileɣ n terbaɛt-agi.
D Guillaume Mulak ara d-yelhin s usileɣ n yimurar ilmeẓyen ara d-tettrebbi terbaɛt-agi n yilmeẓyen n Leqbayel deg wammas anaddal, ara yilin deg tama n Wad Ɛisi.
